---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
title: "Privacy Policy"
description: "Read the privacy policy for Astro AI."
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Read the privacy policy for Astro AI.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Astro AI collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our app and website.</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>Personal information you provide (such as email address, name, etc.)</li>
      <li>Usage data and analytics</li>
      <li>Cookies and similar technologies</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>To provide and improve our services</li>
      <li>To communicate with you</li>
      <li>To ensure security and prevent fraud</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>Access, update, or delete your personal information</li>
      <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
      <li>Request information about our data practices</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-4">For any questions or requests regarding your privacy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@astroai.app" class="text-primary underline">support@astroai.app</a>.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-8">This policy may be updated from time to time. Please review it regularly.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
